In the MATTER OF the Imprisonment of: Jashawn A. SUMMERS No. 387P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 2, 2018 Jashawn A. Summers, for Summers, Jashawn A. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 2nd of November 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Forsyth County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 2nd of November 2018."
